  "title": "Pet groomer",
  "description": "<p>Hiring: Pet Groomer (Singapore)</p><p>Location: Singapore</p><p>Employment Type: Full-time / Part-time</p><p>Salary: Competitive, based on experience + incentives</p><p></p><p>About Us</p><p>We are a friendly and growing pet grooming salon in Singapore, dedicated to providing safe, gentle, and high-quality grooming services for pets. We’re looking for a passionate Pet Groomer who truly loves animals and takes pride in their work.</p><p></p><p>Job Responsibilities</p><p>Perform professional grooming services (bathing, drying, trimming, styling) for dogs and/or cats</p><p></p><p>Handle pets calmly and safely, ensuring their comfort at all times</p><p></p><p>Assess pet coat and skin condition and recommend appropriate grooming care</p><p></p><p>Maintain cleanliness and hygiene of grooming tools and work areas</p><p></p><p>Provide friendly customer service and communicate clearly with pet owners</p><p></p><p>Requirements</p><p>Prior experience as a pet groomer preferred (training can be provided for junior roles)</p><p></p><p>Genuine love for animals and patience in handling pets</p><p></p><p>Knowledge of basic grooming techniques and pet safety</p><p></p><p>Responsible, punctual, and a team player</p><p></p><p>Relevant grooming certification is an advantage</p><p></p><p>What We Offer</p><p>Competitive salary with performance incentives</p><p></p><p>Supportive and pet-loving work environment 🐶🐱</p><p></p><p>Opportunities for skills upgrading and career growth</p><p></p><p>Staff discounts on grooming products and services</p><p></p><p>How to Apply</p><p>Interested candidates, please WhatsApp / email your resume and portfolio (if available).</p><p>Shortlisted candidates will be contacted for an interview.</p>",
